MESSAGE.value:
Initial commit
This is just real basic stuff, nothing interesting.

Add basic firmware entry point
More to come...

Check the CLRC663 device version after init
If we check the CLRC663 device version at device init time, the clock configuration will be inaccurate due to board errata. We need to wait until the clock configuration is set before talking to the device.

Remove HAL_ prefixes
It's getting too verbose.
Enable RF field and set CLRC663 SPI SCLK to 4MHz
Handle the "UART" one byte at a time for now
